  <summary date="2020-05-05T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Federal Frontline Worker Leave Protection Act

This bill restores annual leave that is lost by federal employees who respond to the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) pandemic.

The bill applies retroactively.</summary>
